.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-DELETE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-delete \- permanently delete a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-delete
.I wallet_name
.RB [ --force ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Deletes the wallet directory and all its contents.
Requires
.B --force
to confirm the destructive operation.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"status":"deleted","wallet":"<name>"}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-list (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-rename (1)
